---

---

<section id="details" class="info-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="info-header">
            <h2 class="info-title">
                Todo lo que necesitas saber sobre la Masterclass
            </h2>
            <div class="info-divider"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid content-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-header">
                    <img
                        src="/images/img_icon_lime_50_24x24.svg"
                        alt="Para quién es"
                        class="info-card-icon"
                    />
                    <h3 class="info-card-title">
                        Este programa es para vos si:
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card-list">
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <img
                            src="/images/img_margin_lime_50.svg"
                            alt="Bullet point"
                            class="info-card-bullet"
                        />
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Sentís que sostenés mucho y querés volver a tu eje.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <img
                            src="/images/img_margin_lime_50.svg"
                            alt="Bullet point"
                            class="info-card-bullet"
                        />
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Querés un cambio real con método y continuidad.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <img
                            src="/images/img_margin_lime_50.svg"
                            alt="Bullet point"
                            class="info-card-bullet"
                        />
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Te interesa crecer en madurez emocional y autoconocimiento.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <img
                            src="/images/img_margin_lime_50.svg"
                            alt="Bullet point"
                            class="info-card-bullet"
                        />
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Estás dispuesta a hacer el proceso: escuchar, trabajar, integrar y sostener.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-header">
                    <svg class="info-card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5c5ba" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                        <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="info-card-title">No es para vos si:</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card-list">
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <svg class="info-card-bullet-cross" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5c5ba" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                            <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Buscás una solución rápida sin continuidad.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <svg class="info-card-bullet-cross" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5c5ba" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                            <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Querés cambiar tu vida sin revisar hábitos, decisiones y patrones.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <svg class="info-card-bullet-cross" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5c5ba" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                            <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Te sirve más el entretenimiento que el trabajo interno.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card results-card">
                <div class="info-card-header">
                    <svg class="info-card-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9e8b7f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle>
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="info-card-title">Los resultados que vas a obtener:</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card-list results-list">
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Recuperar claridad mental y dirección interna.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Tomar decisiones con más calma y menos culpa.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Dejar de vivir en modo reacción.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Fortalecer autoestima y autovaloración.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Ordenar tiempo, prioridades y energía.</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-item">
                        <span class="info-card-dot"></span>
                        <span class="info-card-text"
                            >Construir cambios sostenibles (no impulsos).</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
